Package: spAbundance
Type: Package
Title: Single-Species and Multi-Species Spatial Abundance Models 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Jeffrey Doser [aut, cre], Andrew Finley [aut]
Maintainer: "Jeffrey Doser [aut, cre]" <doserjef@msu.edu>
Description: Fits single-species and multi-species non-spatial and spatial abundance models in a Bayesian framework using Markov Chain Monte Carlo (MCMC). 
